  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔥 Devil Dead – Face the Hordes of Hell! 🔥</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gates of <strong>Hell</strong> have opened, and Avalon is under siege! Step into the chaos in this <strong>2D horror arcade action platformer</strong>, where every battle pushes you closer to the ultimate showdown with the Devil himself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>Battle Through Legendary Landscapes:</strong><br>Fight across the <strong>Cemetery of the Damned</strong>, the <strong>Haunted Forest</strong>, the <strong>Doomed Ancient Caves</strong>, scorching <strong>Lava Caverns</strong>, eerie <strong>Sleepless Night Fields</strong>, the <strong>Fields of Avalon</strong>, the cursed <strong>Castle</strong>, and finally, the depths of <strong>Hell</strong> itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <strong>Unleash Magic & Skills:</strong><br>Master devastating <strong>attack spells</strong>, summon <strong>defensive wards</strong>, and unlock <strong>epic abilities</strong> to crush demons and survive the nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👹 <strong>Arcade-Style Action:</strong><br>Fast-paced combat, relentless waves of enemies, and classic platforming challenges — all packed into a dark, medieval horror atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your destiny: <strong>defeat the demons, slay the Devil, and free Avalon from eternal damnation.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The kingdom won’t save itself… are you ready?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔥 Devil Dead – Face the Hordes of Hell! 🔥</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gates of <strong>Hell</strong> have opened, and Avalon is under siege! Step into the chaos in this <strong>2D horror arcade action platformer</strong>, where every battle pushes you closer to the ultimate showdown with the Devil himself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>Battle Through Legendary Landscapes:</strong><br>Fight across the <strong>Cemetery of the Damned</strong>, the <strong>Haunted Forest</strong>, the <strong>Doomed Ancient Caves</strong>, scorching <strong>Lava Caverns</strong>, eerie <strong>Sleepless Night Fields</strong>, the <strong>Fields of Avalon</strong>, the cursed <strong>Castle</strong>, and finally, the depths of <strong>Hell</strong> itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <strong>Unleash Magic & Skills:</strong><br>Master devastating <strong>attack spells</strong>, summon <strong>defensive wards</strong>, and unlock <strong>epic abilities</strong> to crush demons and survive the nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👹 <strong>Arcade-Style Action:</strong><br>Fast-paced combat, relentless waves of enemies, and classic platforming challenges — all packed into a dark, medieval horror atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your destiny: <strong>defeat the demons, slay the Devil, and free Avalon from eternal damnation.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The kingdom won’t save itself… are you ready?</p>",
